{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Following prior research (Alekseeva et al., 2021), we used a detailed taxonomy of AI skills and competencies (Appendix A) and tested whether an executive possessed skills and competencies from the taxonomy.",
    "We view an executive as AI-literate if they possess at least one entry (out of 71) from the taxonomy.",
    "A firm's TMT AI literacy is then measured with the share of AI-literate executives on the firm's TMT.",
    "As such, the measure ranges between 0 and 1.",
    "We followed prior research in operationalizing our measurement of AI orientation (Li et al., 2021)."
  ],
